Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:26.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}心に　授かった祈りを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:32.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}傷つけられないくらいに記憶の底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.07,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}刻み込まれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.25,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Let’s start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.90,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}さあ運命越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}I will take it…over！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}自分のために生きるこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}手を伸ばしたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:56.53,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}確かめるように思い出して We’re dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}迷わないように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.89,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}ならせ鼓動　空に願う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}信じた未来に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:10.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}立ち上がるたびに見渡して　居場所を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}常識を塗り替えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}これは一から始まるストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}はて無き道を駆けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:28.24,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}目指してるのは見た事ない世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:26.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}将这份心灵的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:32.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}深深地刻在记忆深处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}谁也无法伤害到分寸
Comment: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}Let’s start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}超脱命运
Comment: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}I will take it…over！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}在这为自己而活的世界之巅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}伸手向前不断进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:56.53,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}回想起来吧 We’re dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不再迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}让心跳轰鸣  向天空许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}触碰这自己所坚信的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:10.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}每次站起之时所环顾的这只属于自己的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}重新定义常识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}这是从零开始的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.65,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}在着无尽的道路上奔跑向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:28.24,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我们追求的就是那未曾知晓的世界
Comment: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:35.17,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}目覚まし勝利して聞くテーマソング
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:39.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}今日の一歩目歩んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:45.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}出かける前が大事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}何を着ても似合ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}自信以外の荷物はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}セルフハグ・ビッグラヴ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.70,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}お気に入りの私でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:08.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}I will take me everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:15.58,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}戦う私　傷ひとつなくみえるでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:22.38,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}悪くないこの体　抱きしめてみた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:25.01,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}キラキラしなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:27.38,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}華やかなじゃなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}わすれないで　おっきな愛を
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.91,0:22:35.17,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}睁开双眼 传来了胜利的旋律
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.17,0:22:39.21,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}踏出今天的第一步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.63,0:22:45.93,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}出门前的准备可是很重要的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.89,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}无论穿什么都非常合适
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.94,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}只需要带着这份自信就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.48,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}Selfhug Biglove
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.70,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}只想保持着这真实的自我
Comment: 1,0:23:05.99,0:23:08.45,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}I will take me everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.66,0:23:15.58,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}几经沙场的我也是如此的可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.21,0:23:22.38,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}拥抱这还算不错的身体
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.38,0:23:25.01,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}即便没有动人心弦的身姿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.01,0:23:27.38,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}也没有华丽的外表
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.93,ED_CH,,0,0,56,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur2}也不要忘记 这份自爱
